rows.label: qst640301_msg0001
rows.name:
I like it up here.
This view over Teos Aure is
simply unparalleled...

rows.label: qst640301_msg0003
rows.name: I know where you were going with it...

rows.label: qst640301_msg0004
rows.name:
You want me, the greatest artisan on
Alst, to make you, a random person,
an accessory made of Ripbik Ellook.

rows.label: qst640301_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, I'm going home. Don't bother
me until you can show me some prime
Ellook Horn!

rows.label: qst640301_msg0006
rows.name: And don't make me wait too long.
